---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — Curiosity Log"
  description="A minimalist inquiry into the mechanics of the everyday. We document the things often overlooked, seeking meaning in the mundane."
>
  <div class="about-page">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/" class="back-link">
        <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"/>
        </svg>
        Back to Journal
      </a>

      <div class="about-content">
        <header class="about-header">
          <p class="label">About</p>
          <h1 class="about-heading">Observatory of the Ordinary</h1>
          <div class="accent-line"></div>
        </header>

        <div class="about-body">
          <section class="about-section">
            <h2>What This Is</h2>
            <p>Curiosity Log is a quiet place on the internet for small, careful questions. The kind you ask yourself in the shower or while staring at something unremarkable — and then can't stop thinking about.</p>
            <p>Each entry begins with an observation, follows it down, and tries to find the thing underneath. Why do we do this? Where does this come from? What does this tell us about everything else?</p>
          </section>

          <section class="about-section">
            <h2>The Philosophy</h2>
            <p>The everyday is full of compressed history. A handshake contains centuries of diplomacy. A bento box contains principles of geometry and restraint. A towel contains assumptions about the human body that nobody ever wrote down.</p>
            <p>We believe the most interesting ideas are the ones hiding in plain sight — in the textures of daily life that we have all agreed, without discussion, to stop noticing.</p>
          </section>

          <section class="about-section">
            <h2>How to Read It</h2>
            <p>There is no schedule. Entries appear when they're ready. They are written to be read slowly, once, and then thought about again later while you're doing something else entirely.</p>
            <p>If something stays with you, that's the point.</p>
          </section>

          <section class="about-section">
            <h2>Subscribe</h2>
            <p>New entries are available via <a href="/rss.xml" class="inline-link">RSS feed</a>. Add it to your feed reader and it will arrive like a letter — unannounced, whenever it's ready.</p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding-top: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 5);
    padding-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 16);
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: calc(var(--spacing-unit));
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 8);
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .about-content {
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .about-header {
    padding-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 8);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 10);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--divider);
  }

  .about-header .label {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 3);
  }

  .about-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 4);
  }

  .accent-line {
    width: 40px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .about-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 10);
  }

  .about-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 4);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 2);
  }

  .about-section h2::before {
    content: '';
    display: inline-block;
    width: 24px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .about-section p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 3);
  }

  .about-section p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .inline-link {
    color: var(--text);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent);
    padding-bottom: 1px;
    transition: color 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .inline-link:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .about-heading {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
    }

    .about-content {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
